---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Wordmark from '../components/Wordmark.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Oxygn — The cost of building collapsed. The cost of thinking didn't."
  description="Oxygn is building the operating system for a world where a single person can run a billion-dollar company."
>

  <div class="breath" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main class="shell">

    <header class="topbar">
      <a href="/" aria-label="Oxygn home" class="topbar-mark">
        <Wordmark size="0.9rem" />
      </a>
      <span class="topbar-meta">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span>Manifesto</span>
      </span>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <h1 class="hero-title" id="hero-title">
        <span class="hero-line">The cost of <em>building</em></span>
        <span class="hero-line">collapsed to zero.</span>
        <span class="hero-line">The cost of <em>thinking</em> didn&rsquo;t.</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="hero-foot">
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Oxygn is building the operating system for a world where a single
          person can run a billion-dollar company.
        </p>
        <a class="hero-cue" href="#shift">
          <span class="cue-bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span>Read the manifesto</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <article class="act" id="shift">
      <header class="act-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">I &nbsp;·&nbsp; The shift</span>
        <h2 class="act-title">
          The bottleneck<br/>
          moved from <em>execution</em><br/>
          to <em>ideation</em>.
        </h2>
      </header>

      <blockquote class="pull">
        For two centuries, the hard part was making things. Now the hard part
        is deciding what is worth making.
      </blockquote>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Planning the factory, writing the code, onboarding the team —
          these were the rate-limiters of value. They aren&rsquo;t any more.
          The marginal cost of execution has fallen below the marginal cost
          of a good idea.
        </p>
        <p>
          Knowledge workers stop being builders and become <em>ideators</em>.
          Their output is taste: which ideas to test, which to kill, which
          to ship. Everything downstream is automation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Human creativity has not become less valuable. It has become the
          only remaining constraint.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="act">
      <header class="act-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">II &nbsp;·&nbsp; The company</span>
        <h2 class="act-title">
          The company<br/>
          as <em>prompt library</em>,<br/>
          run by <em>one person</em>.
        </h2>
      </header>

      <blockquote class="pull">
        The org chart replaced by an ever-evolving library of prompts, and a
        single curator with taste.
      </blockquote>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          A traditional company is a structure of people executing processes.
          A post-AI company is a network of prompts that execute themselves —
          small adaptive specialists that together form an entity which
          learns, prunes, and grows without meetings.
        </p>
        <p>
          When execution is free, you don&rsquo;t need a workforce. You need
          a <em>curator</em>. One person orchestrates a library of autonomous
          agents that cover operations, research, sales, customer service,
          capital allocation — everything.
        </p>
        <p>
          The upper bound of what one person could build was set by how many
          people they could coordinate. That constraint is gone. The new
          upper bound is <em>imagination</em>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="act">
      <header class="act-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">III &nbsp;·&nbsp; In practice</span>
        <h2 class="act-title">
          Where this<br/>
          is <em>real</em>.
        </h2>
      </header>

      <ol class="cases">
        <li class="case">
          <span class="case-num">i</span>
          <div class="case-body">
            <h3>Risk management in financial services</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">
              An AI system that reviews, challenges, and documents every risk
              in a regulated fund manager&rsquo;s risk register — two hundred
              risks assessed in under an hour, each through a six-step
              adversarial workflow. Regulatory citations verified against
              actual instruments. Every step produces an immutable audit
              trail. The system forces its own reasoning to be challenged
              before anything is published.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="case">
          <span class="case-num">ii</span>
          <div class="case-body">
            <h3>Managing customer terms and conditions</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">
              An interview-driven assessment engine that ingests legal
              documents — terms, conditions, policies, contracts — from any
              source, classifies every assertion by epistemic status,
              identifies risks across twelve categories, and challenges its
              own findings against eleven criteria before publishing.
              Defensible enough for a regulatory exam. Fast enough to run
              before a contract is signed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="case">
          <span class="case-num">iii</span>
          <div class="case-body">
            <h3>Building an AI-first organisation</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">
              A complete organisational architecture for a multi-jurisdiction
              financial services firm, designed from first principles around
              AI agents as the default workers. Twenty-five specialist agents
              execute eighty capabilities. Eight verification agents
              cross-check critical decisions. Thirty to forty humans focus on
              strategy, regulatory relationships, and crisis response. Four
              autonomy tiers govern what agents may do — and a documented
              process upgrades those boundaries as trust is earned.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </article>

    <section class="closing" aria-labelledby="closing-title">
      <span class="eyebrow">The mission</span>
      <p class="closing-title" id="closing-title">
        Oxygn enables<br/>
        <em>infinitely scaled</em><br/>
        human productivity.
      </p>
      <p class="closing-tag">Massively more.&nbsp;&nbsp;Vastly less.</p>

      <div class="founder">
        <div class="founder-head">
          <div class="sig-name">James Shanahan</div>
          <div class="sig-role">CEO &amp; Founder, Oxygn</div>
        </div>
        <p class="founder-bio">
          Every financial institution that scales rebuilds the same
          functions — compliance, finance, governance, marketing,
          operations, risk — and staffs each one from scratch. The cost
          scales linearly. The output doesn&rsquo;t. This is the problem
          Oxygn is built to eliminate.
        </p>
        <p class="founder-bio">
          Fintechs proved that financial services reduces to data and
          brand. AI completes the argument: organic, supervised systems
          that deliver what presents as commodity infrastructure —
          differentiated by brand, reliability, and a step-change in value
          to the customer.
        </p>
        <p class="founder-bio">
          Fourteen countries. Every shape of financial institution from
          neobank to insurer to sovereign fund.
        </p>
        <p class="founder-location">Based in Abu Dhabi.</p>
      </div>

      <a class="closing-link" href="mailto:hello@oxygn.xyz">
        Get in touch
        <span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;→</span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <footer class="foot">
      <div class="foot-row">
        <Wordmark size="0.7rem" sup={false} />
        <span>© Oxygn</span>
      </div>
      <div class="foot-row">
        <span>oxygn.xyz&nbsp;&nbsp;·&nbsp;&nbsp;v0.1.0</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/oxygn-cloud-ai/website-xyz" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Source&nbsp;↗</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </main>

</Base>

<style>
  /* ─── Shell ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .shell {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.25rem var(--gutter) 3rem;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ─── Topbar ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .topbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-block: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .topbar-mark {
    line-height: 0.9;
    transition: opacity 400ms ease;
  }
  .topbar-mark:hover { opacity: 0.6; }
  .topbar-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--subtle);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 0.45em;
    height: 0.45em;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 74, 28, 0.08);
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50%      { opacity: 0.25; transform: scale(0.65); }
  }

  /* ─── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 6rem) clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    max-width: 62rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7.5vw, 6.25rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .hero-title .hero-line { display: block; }
  .hero-title .hero-line:nth-child(2) {
    padding-left: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero-foot {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 66ch;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 820px) {
    .hero-foot {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 3rem;
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.35vw, 1.18rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 44ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .hero-cue {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--subtle);
    width: fit-content;
    transition: color 400ms ease;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  .hero-cue:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .cue-bar {
    position: relative;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--mute);
    display: block;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cue-bar::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    animation: slide 3.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes slide {
    0%   { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    50%  { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  }

  /* ─── Act ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .act {
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 8rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    max-width: 62ch;
  }
  .act-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    color: var(--subtle);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .act-title {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4.75vw, 3.75rem);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .act-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ─── Pull quote ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pull {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.1vw, 1.55rem);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 44ch;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--accent);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  /* ─── Prose ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .prose {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.95em;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }
  .prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(0.97rem, 1.25vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .prose em {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05em;
  }

  /* ─── Cases ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cases {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    margin-top: clamp(0.25rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
  }
  .case {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr;
    column-gap: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1.5rem);
    padding-block: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .cases li:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--faint);
  }
  .case-num {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--step-2);
    color: var(--mute);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .case-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .case-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(0.97rem, 1.25vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--subtle);
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
    max-width: 52ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  /* ─── Closing ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .closing {
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    justify-items: start;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }
  .closing-title {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4.75vw, 3.75rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 18ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }
  .closing-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .closing-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--mute);
  }
  .founder {
    margin-top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 48ch;
  }
  .founder-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }
  .sig-name {
    font-family: var(--font-editorial);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.75vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .sig-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--subtle);
  }
  .founder-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(0.92rem, 1.2vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .founder-location {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--subtle);
  }
  .closing-link {
    margin-top: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding-bottom: 0.12rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    transition: color 300ms ease, border-color 300ms ease;
  }
  .closing-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ─── Footer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .foot {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--subtle);
  }
  .foot-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .foot-row a {
    color: var(--subtle);
    transition: color 300ms ease;
  }
  .foot-row a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  /* ─── Breath ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .breath {
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: min(78vh, 78vw);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.11);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
    animation: breath 11s cubic-bezier(.45, 0, .55, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes breath {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);    opacity: 0.55; }
    50%      { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1);  opacity: 0.9; }
  }

  /* ─── Entrance ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .shell > * {
    animation: rise 900ms cubic-bezier(.2, .85, .25, 1) both;
  }
  .shell > :nth-child(1) { animation-delay:   0ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(2) { animation-delay:  80ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 380ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 460ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 540ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 620ms; }
  .shell > :nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 700ms; }
  .hero-title .hero-line {
    animation: rise 1000ms cubic-bezier(.18, .88, .22, 1) both;
  }
  .hero-title .hero-line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 180ms; }
  .hero-title .hero-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 300ms; }
  .hero-title .hero-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 420ms; }

  @keyframes rise {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0.6rem); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .breath { display: none; }
  }
</style>
